.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: water-polo, snowboarding, skiing, volleyball, rowing, parkour, badminton
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
3. the person who's sport is skiing is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
5. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
6. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
8. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |    3     |    4     |   5    |     6      |  7   |
| Sport   | water-polo | badminton | volleyball | parkour | rowing | skiing | snowboarding |

