4. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
6. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the person who's sport is baseball##3
7. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far left##1
8. the person who's sport is sailing is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |      2       |     3      |     4      |    5    |     6      |     7      |
| Sport   | badminton | lacrosse | skateboarding | baseball | tennis | soccer | sailing |

