.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-7::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: juice, iced-tea, hot-chocolate, milk, sprite, cola, fanta
1. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person drinking cola is in the middle##1
3. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
4. the person drinking milk is the person drinking milk##1
5. the person drinking fanta is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person drinking cola##2
6. the person drinking fanta is in an odd position##4
7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |    2    |    3     |  4  |   5   |    6     |   7    |
| Beverage   | juice | milk | sprite | cola | fanta | hot-chocolate | iced-tea |

