.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-8::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: card-games, collecting, photography, filmmaking, video-games, magic-tricks, dancing
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
4. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
5. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##3
6. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an odd position##4
7. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
8. the person who's hobby is dancing is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |   2    |   3    |     4     |    5    |      6      |    7    |
| Hobby   | collecting | card-games | filmmaking | magic-tricks | photography | dancing | video-games |

