.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-9::.
7 different pets are kept: pony, ferret, frog, guinea-pig, cat, mouse, hamster
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
3. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
4. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
5. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
6. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
7. the owner of the hamster is in an even position##4
8. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
9. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |   2   |     3      |   4    |   5    |  6   |   7   |
| Pet   | frog | hamster | pony | cat | mouse | ferret | guinea-pig |

