.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-10::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: reggae, trance, dubstep, techno, hip-hop, house, metal
1. the fan of house is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
2. the fan of techno is on the far left##1
3. the fan of metal is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3
4. the fan of dubstep is in the middle##1
5. the fan of metal is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
6. the fan of reggae is in an even position##4
7. the fan of techno is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |  3   |  4   |  5   |     6     |  7  |
| Music-Genre   | techno | hip-hop | trance | dubstep | metal | reggae | house |

