.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-13::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: quad-bike, bus, scooter, helicopter, boat, roller, bike
1. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
2. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
4. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
5. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3
6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
7. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
8. the person driving the bus is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2   |  3   |   4    |   5   |  6  |  7  |
| Transport   | bus | helicopter | boat | scooter | roller | bike | quad-bike |

