.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-20::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: scooter, van, car, bus, roller, skateboard, motorbike
 1. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
 2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 3. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
 4. the person driving the roller is in an odd position##4
 5. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3
 6. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the car##1
 7. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
 8. the person driving the skateboard is in an odd position##4
 9. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
10. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |  2   |  3   |  4   |     5      |     6     |  7   |
| Transport   | van | scooter | motorbike | bus | roller | car | skateboard |

 